text: Hey @FedEx please don't leave a package status sticker on my door that says a package will be available at a pickup site at 6 and have me drive 5 miles across town to find out that the package won't ACTUALLY be there until after 9 (when you're closed).

@SKutnicki Hello, this is Gaylen. Would you like help with tracking your package?Please DM your name, address, city, state, zip code, tracking number, phone number, and email address. https://t.co/7vnSkvqx3r

@FedExHelp Thanks, but I already did that with the app and that's what indicated to me that I could in fact pick it up at the shipping center. When I arrived they said that truck was still out and that the app info must have been an error.
@SKutnicki I am so sorry this happened. Please let us know if we can assist in the future. -Gaylen
